HEADWORD: Monogenist
<hw>Mo*nog"e*nist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Anthropol.)</fld> <def>One who maintains that the human races are
all of one species; -- opposed to <contr>polygenist</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monogenistic</ent>⟦br⟧
